ld you look at to determin...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When evaluating the results of a study you read about, what factors would you look at to determine if it describes a reliable finding?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q22","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ESTB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When evaluating the results of a study you read about, what factors would you look at to determin...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"QuestionID":"QID22"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1Opo4nmrQFts3RP","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID19","SecondaryAttribute":"Why do you think there is a replication crisis in psychology?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Why do you think there is a replication crisis in psychology?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q19","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"ESTB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Why do you think there is a replication crisis in psychology?","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"QuestionID":"QID19"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1Opo4nmrQFts3RP","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID35","SecondaryAttribute":"You have reached the end of the survey. Please enter your MSU NetID (i.e., your email address) as...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"You have reached the end of the survey. Please enter your MSU NetID (i.e., your email address) as proof of completion of the survey.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q36","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You have reached the end of the survey. Please enter your MSU NetID (i.e., your email address) as...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"Non